<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1290900>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–12. Acmaeodera (Ptychomus) argodi Kerremans, 1907 species-group, habitus. Fig. 1, A. kubani kubani subsp. nov., holotype, ♂, Algeria (VKCB), dorsal aspect, 5.6 mm; Fig. 5, the same, paratype, ♂, Egypt (ZIN), lateral aspect, 5.8 mm; Fig. 9, the same, ventral aspect; Fig. 2, A. kubani saudita subsp. nov., holotype, ♂, Saudi Arabia (NMPC), dorsal aspect, 5.2 mm; Fig. 6, the same, paratype, ♂, Saudi Arabia (ZIN), lateral aspect, 5.3 mm; Fig. 10, the same, ventral aspect; Fig. 3, A. argodi Kerremans, 1907, ♂specimen, Somali (ZIN), dorsal aspect, 5.8 mm; Fig. 7, the same, lateral aspect; Fig. 11, the same, ventral aspect; Fig. 4, A. cupreosuturata Obst, 1903, ♂specimen, Kenya (ZIN), dorsal aspect, 5.1 mm; Fig. 8, the same, lateral aspect; Fig. 12, the same, ventral aspect." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1290900/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1290902>
    dc:description "FIGURES 13–16. Acmaeodera (Ptychomus) kubani sp. nov., head and pronotum. Fig. 13, A. kubani kubani subsp. nov., paratype, ♂, Egypt (ZIN), head and pronotum, frontal aspect; Fig. 15, the same, dorsal aspect; Fig. 14, A. kubani saudita subsp. nov., paratype, ♂, Saudi Arabia (ZIN), head and pronotum, frontal aspect; Fig. 16, the same, dorsal aspect." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1290902/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1290904>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17–22. Acmaeodera (Ptychomus) kubani sp. nov., prosternum and appendages. Fig. 17, A. kubani kubani subsp. nov., paratype, ♂, Egypt (ZIN), head and prosternum, ventral aspect; Fig. 19, the same, right antenna; Fig. 20, the same, right fore-leg; Fig. 21, the same, mid-leg; Fig. 22, the same, hind-leg; Fig. 18, A. kubani saudita subsp. nov., paratype, ♂, Saudi Arabia (ZIN), head and prosternum, ventral aspect." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1290904/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1290906>
    dc:description "FIGURES 23–33. Acmaeodera (Ptychomus) argodi Kerremans, 1907 species-group, male and female genitalia. Fig. 23, A. kubani kubani subsp. nov., paratype, ♂, Egypt (ZIN), microslide no. 1537, tegmen, 1.3 mm; Fig. 24, the same, penis, 0.9 mm; Fig. 31, paratype, ♀, Egypt (ZIN), microslide no. 1921, ovipositor, 1.0 mm; Fig. 32, the same, ventrite 8, 0.3 mm; Fig. 33, the same, tergite 8, 1.0 mm; Fig. 25, A. kubani saudita subsp. nov., paratype, ♂, Saudi Arabia (ZIN),), microslide no. 1536, tegmen, 1.3 mm; Fig. 26, the same, penis, 0.9 mm; Fig. 27, A. argodi Kerremans, 1907, ♂specimen, Somali (ZIN), microslide no. 1892, tegmen, 1.4 mm; Fig. 28, the same, penis, 0.9 mm; Fig. 29, A. cupreosuturata Obst, 1903, ♂specimen, Kenya (ZIN), microslide no. 1891, tegmen, 1.4 mm; Fig. 30, the same, penis, 0.9 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1290906/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

